I=\int_{0}^{\pi}\frac{x\tan (x)}{\tan(x)+\sec(x)}dx 
\int_{0}^{\pi}\frac{\pi-x\tan (x)}{\tan(x)+\sec(x)}dx 
2I=\int_{0}^{\pi}\frac{\pi\tan (x)}{\tan(x)+\sec(x)}dx=\pi\int_{0}^{\pi}\frac{sin (x)}{sin(x)+1}dx
\sec x-\tan x
